result.notes:
Current (undetermined) and most recent 100 days of determined applications at Mole Valley District Council, Surrey, UK.  Data updated daily.  Data formatted according to ODUG national schema, see: http://schemas.opendata.esd.org.uk/PlanningApplications.  Also available as GeoRSS, XML and CSV.  To save as CSV use CSV download link and 'save page as' .CSV for correct comma separated formatting.  This will provide you with a neatly formatted CSV file which can be opened in a spreadsheet package such as Excel or Libre Office Calc

PSMA End User licence: http://www.ordnancesurvey.co.uk/business-and-government/public-sector/mapping-agreements/end-user-licence.html

Data can be visualised and accessed for whole of Surrey County (including APIs) here: http://digitalservices.surreyi.gov.uk/
